    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The CNN surrogate demonstrated consistent RHI predictions across two independent training runs (seed A: MAE 0.031, seed B: MAE 0.033), and bench validation confirmed MIH predictions within the ±20% acceptance criterion. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The assessment team concluded that the evidence package provides adequate credibility for the intended use of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
